title: [1980] From PSYOP to MindWar - The Psychology of Victory.pdf
description: "From PSYOP to Mindwar: The Psychology of Victory" is a military paper on psychological warfare, written by Lt. Col. Michael Aquino and Col. Paul E. Vallely in 1980. It was sent to various governmental offices, agencies, commands and publications involved or interested in PSYOP. It describes a top-down psychological conditioning Americans may find familiar.
